arStrings.szText: Your skills gain a {c_random}[Affix_Value_1|%+2|]{/c} Critical Strike Chance bonus per point of Primary Resource you have, up to {c_random}[100*Affix_Value_1|%+|]{/c}. Each point of Primary Resource above {c_number}100{/c} grants {c_number}[Affix."Static Value 0"|1%x|]{/c} Critical Strike Damage instead.
